  "body": "Skeleton issue. Awaiting PR.\r\n\r\n### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I want to discover screens to look pretty like in the design so that using discover is a delight.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: There are a number of discrepancies between the design and Discover. The goal of this issue is to capture the main ones for: Main Screen (empty states)\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1552237/31394509-cd264c36-adde-11e7-9824-9145297176a9.png)\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1552237/31394519-d2480934-adde-11e7-9fc4-3518d200372f.png)\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1552237/31604061-72b692be-b262-11e7-9c93-bda709dbaa35.png)\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1552237/31604070-79deb7e2-b262-11e7-9bf3-2012d3e4b505.png)\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1552237/31604073-7ee3c7d2-b262-11e7-909c-ee5a2be93c2e.png)\r\n\r\n#### List of things to fix (non-exhaustive)\r\n\r\n## Must have\r\n- [ ] Too wide top margin toolbar ( for iOS it should be 76, for android 80, check other tabs in our app please) (Oskar done in checkout, PR coming Oct 17)\r\n- [ ] *Goran* If can fix in 1 hr do it otherwise move to nice to have  -  All content hidden behind right edge on smaller screen (check 5s)\r\n\r\n## Nice  have\r\n- [ ] Font weight \"Recent statuses\" etc bolder \r\n- [ ]  Titles for sections should be without letter spacing\r\n- [ ] \"No statuses text\" should be grey ( color-gray4 [#939BA1] )\r\n- [ ] Reduce size between title Dapps and dapps icons. it should be 24px\r\n- [ ] Names os public chats are too bold, they need medium font weight\r\n- [ ] Let's add a stroke to dapps icons. It will be much better with it. Use color: color-gray-transparent-light \r\n- [ ] improve the central alignment of empty state. Move icon a bit up\r\n- [ ] check dapp name font size. In the mocks it's 14. \r\n\r\n- [ ] UI checklist\r\n- [ ] Check Android",
